    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "\"Actually he can be very sweet.\nJust\nescort him to the lounge, give him a\ncocktail, some hot hors d'ourves and\ntell him the 40 hour week started this\ncountry on the road to ruin.\"",
      "TIT GE\n\"The company plane is always\nat my disposal, of course-\nBut there's no lounge!\"",
      "\"Personally, I think it's poor form to spend\nall of one's time in the club bar.\"\nUnited AirLines\nThe\nClub Commuter\nCLOSE COVER BEFORE STRIKING",
